name: BoxCycle
overview:
BoxCycle is an online marketplace for used boxes. It connects retailers, recyclers, box manufacturers and others for whom used boxes are a hassle with people looking for moving, shipping, or storage boxes.

For sellers, BoxCycle locates buyers, handles communication, sets up appointments, and collects payment. BoxCycle eliminates common time sinks that dissuade busy businesses from getting their boxes reused. Through BoxCycle businesses can help the environment and their community while reducing their box hassles and getting paid for their effort.

For buyers, BoxCycle provides hassle-free access to inexpensive used box sources including actual seller inventory. Buyers reserve their boxes online by setting up an appointment and paying for their purchase. Buyers can pickup their boxes in hours from sellers closest to them.
